edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=rCC6LyfnNA3Id4pBenNlAf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1598c586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"d9f8ecd2829130a13bc72bb61117ae9bd6f03ced","tid":970454,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"朝早嗰時仲覺得無乜嘢，一到半夜，忍唔住喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5634ed8b2b4d7d841635e5145ac0c1bc250b58a","tid":970454,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f8ecd2829130a13bc72bb61117ae9bd6f03ced","tid":970454,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"朝早嗰時仲覺得無乜嘢，一到半夜，忍唔住喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"有咩心事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪又係一到夜晚就亂諗野"},{"pid":"0288661ec3e5458224c54dc4a710482527b298f9","tid":970454,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5634ed8b2b4d7d841635e5145ac0c1bc250b58a","tid":970454,"uid":220305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f8ecd2829130a13bc72bb61117ae9bd6f03ced","tid":970454,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"朝早嗰時仲覺得無乜嘢，一到半夜，忍唔住喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"有咩心事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /